reviewText: I loved "My Tutor" and "My Chauffeur" back when they came out.  Was thrilled to find them on DVD.  I don't remember the other 2.  "Tomboy" and "Jocks" are the worst piece of crap I've ever tried to watch.  I lost a couple of hours of my life that I'll never get back.  BUT......the price was great for just 2 movies anyway so it's worth the purchase.
